jobs.name: :police_officer: Police Officer
jobs.info: Be a cop, arrest criminals, raise extra money.

jobs.name: :detective: Police Detective
jobs.info: Stay hidden till the right moment, strike with pleasure and earn even better!

jobs.name: :person_in_tuxedo: Lawyer
jobs.info: You ears are going to ring with `Objection!` and `Order! Order!` if you pick this career.

jobs.name: :judge: Court Judge
jobs.info: Handle legal cases carefully, otherwise end up at the jaws of the Mafia and lose everything you love

jobs.name: :ninja: SWAT
jobs.info: No, you're not a ninja. You're a member of the SWAT. High risk, high pay, high requirements.

jobs.name: :person_in_tuxedo: FBI
jobs.info: Don't expect to be breaking down doors and yelling your iconic bureau's name; most of the time is spent doing heavy research on potential threats
